DEBBIE DARLING bumped with a rival at the start, was urged along on the outside, angled in late on the backstretch, rounded the turn in the two path and was no factor. AERON WARRIOR broke out and bumped with a foe, steadied some while in tight between horses nearing the five-eighths then dropped back, angled in shortly thereafter, raced inside to the two path on the turn and failed to respond.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: CAMM' DUKE vied five paths off the inside down the backstretch before seizing sole command half a mile from home, tucked three wide through the turn, went five wide into upper stretch and went clear under a drive to prevail. FOUR EYES chased four to five wide under coaxing from the seven-sixteenths, swung six wide for home and improved position to secure the place honors. LIEUTENANT SAM vied three to four wide down the backstretch before tucking inside through the turn knocking heads with the eventual winner to the five-sixteenths, swung three wide for home and weakened while along for the show honors. EXCALIBRATE got bumped at the start by CENTRAL LOVE, chased just off the inside until tucked inside through the turn coming under coaxing at the seven-sixteenths, spun two to three wide for home and made no impact. SOMAMA BEACH broke in at the start bumping BUSTINUPISHARDTODO and stumbled when making contact with that foe, chased along the inside coming under coaxing at the seven-sixteenths, angled five wide into upper stretch and made no impact. M. C. DOUBLE R three wide in pursuit, came under coaxing at the three-eighths, angled five wide into upper stretch and tired. MILAGROSO seven paths off the inside down the backstretch, tucked four wide through the turn and came under coaxing at the three-eighths, spun two to three wide into upper stretch and proved no factor.
